<span class="displaytext">las vegas, nv -- (candidate full) made the following statement today on the culinary workers union local 226 and bartenders union local 165 settling their contract with the las vegas hilton. <p>"i am pleased to see that the management at the las vegas hilton has joined with their workers to ensure a fair contract and a living wage for all. with this contract comes the opportunity for these workers to achieve the las vegas dream. </p><p>during these final contract negotiations, i will continue to stand with the culinary union until every last worker has the fair contract they deserve."</p></span>



